							<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Non-combat:
<br />
Without any songs power regeneration is 67 per tick.
<br />
Bria's Stirring Balad (adept I) increases this to 71 per tick.
<br />
Cassindra's Chant of Clarity to 74 per tick.
<br />
The two songs do not stack.
<br />

<br />
Combat:
<br />
Without any songs power regeneration is 9 per tick.
<br />
Bria's Stirring Balad (adept I) increases this to 13 per tick.
<br />
Cassindra's Chant of Clarity to 15 per tick.
<br />
The two songs do not stack.
<br />

<br />
Aegolin, 27 Troubador</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
