							<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Bria's Thrilling Ballad (Adept III) is 9 mana a tick, up from the app1 7 mana a tick. Thrilling Ballad does NOT Stirring ballad. 
<br />

<br />
Yes Cassandra's Chant of Clarity and Bria's Thrilling/stirring Ballad will both stack together, BUT the higher mana regen will take hold over the other, and cassandra's chant still chips in with the Intelligence. This is why some bards become fooled when using these two together, they see both icons on the maintained spell list but do not realize that only one mana regen is working for them.
<br />

<br />
Have yet to get level 30 yet (29 atm) will post the level 30 training options.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
